  "additionalProperties": false,
  "description": "Frozen public request contract.\n\nCompared to the legacy ``SimulationRequest``:\n  - ``panel`` (alias ``panel_de_control``) — required, strict.\n  - ``cadena_a``/``b``/``c`` — optional sections (aliases to the\n    legacy ``condiciones_cadena_*`` keys).\n  - ``cadenas_activas`` — explicit ``Set[Literal[\"A\",\"B\",\"C\"]]``,\n    inferred from contents when omitted (resolves W7-OBS-3).\n  - ``escenarios`` — list of commercial scenarios.\n  - ``metadata`` — optional client/request metadata.",
  "properties": {
    "cadenas_activas": {
      "items": {
        "enum": [
          "A",
          "B",
          "C"
        ],
        "type": "string"
      },
      "title": "Cadenas Activas",
      "type": "array",
      "uniqueItems": true
    },
    "condiciones_cadena_a": {
      "anyOf": [
        {
          "$ref": "#/$defs/CadenaARequestV1"
        },
        {
          "type": "null"
        }
